## 💻 Python API Usage

### Running the Copilot Workflow

```python
import asyncio
from agent import run_agentic_workflow

async def main():
    query = "Why is the Payment API returning a timeout error?"
    response = await run_agentic_workflow(query, thread_id="ticket-1234")
    
    print("Status:", response["status"])
    print("Confidence:", response["confidence_score"])
    print("Answer:", response["final_answer"])

if __name__ == "__main__":
    asyncio.run(main())
```

### Triggering the Feedback Loop

```python
from agent import process_human_feedback

result = process_human_feedback(
    user_query="Payment API timeout error during load",
    final_answer="The Auth Service Redis Cache was stalling. Increased timeout to 500ms.",
    user_id="engineer_jane"
)

print(result["status"])
```

